      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "If I could just suggest a really simply implementation for the time being. Use have a simple `latest_version.txt`  stored on bitcoin.org with the version number. When the bitcoin client loads it can query this file and do a version compare and then notify the user. The command line client could write out message to the console (on startup) if that's OK to do. \n",
